This folder contains the PowerPoint presentation created as part of the Mastercard Cybersecurity Virtual Internship (Forage). The presentation is designed to educate employees about phishing threats and provide practical strategies to avoid falling victim.

---

**Purpose**
The presentation supports the phishing simulation by:

1. Raising awareness of phishing techniques.
2. Highlighting departmental vulnerabilities identified in the campaign.
3. Promoting a security-first culture across the organization.